Ingredients
- 125 g butter
- 125 g brown sugar
- 2 eggs
- 125 g flour
- 1 teaspoon baking powder
- 1 tablespoon cacao
- 3 tablespoons milk
- 200 g chocolate

How to make it
- Preheat the oven to 200 C
- Place cupcake liners in the cupcake tray
- Mix the butter and sugar untill it's airy
- Add the eggs one by one
- Mix it for 2 minutes
- Add the flour, baking powder and cacao and mix untill mixed
- Add the milk and chocolate and mix 
- Divide the mixture in the cupcake liners
- Bake for 15-20 minutes untill done
- Leave them cool in the tray
